# Build-tooling-only CVEs — reviewed 2026-06-18.
#
# tar@6.2.1 and @xmldom/xmldom@0.7.13 are pulled exclusively by packaging tools
# (electron-builder, expo / @expo/cli) and run only on the CI runner during
# `expo export` / `electron-builder`. They never reach a shipped artifact: the Go
# server binary uses no npm, and the Electron app ships only the static web bundle.
# The available fixes are major bumps (tar 6->7, xmldom 0.7->0.9) that those tools
# pin and weren't tested against. Revisit when expo/electron-builder bump them.

# @xmldom/xmldom (via @expo/plist, @electron/osx-sign)
CVE-2026-34601
CVE-2026-41672
CVE-2026-41673
CVE-2026-41674
CVE-2026-41675

# tar (via electron-builder, expo CLI, node-gyp)
